<strong>Reports to CMO</strong></p>
<p>
Heroku is looking for a rock star product marketing manager&nbsp; to help drive the positioning and go-to-market strategy for Heroku&rsquo;s core product. A big part of the job will include partnering with product managers and engineers to bring exceptional product to market, secure user adoption, analyze market opportunities and trends, communicate with users and customers, and, ultimately, drive a set of product marketing programs to deliver pipeline and building best practice tools for our amazing sales and service organizations.</p>
